song_name: I Dreamed There Was No War

version_description: The chords are all correct.  Also, the whole lyrics and order of the song are laid in its entirety.
I wanted to submit the whole song with chords above the words so that it is more easily played using the scroll option. I have also used an set of chords that are best played in DADGAD tuning.

I checked out the other tabs and none of them seemed to have all the right chords, so from the other tabs, an Eagles song book and by listening to the song be played, I'm 99% sure these are the correct chords :)
Capo 2: More original with slight change, but closer to the actual band. Those F#m7 and the F#sus4 make up the featured guitar solos.
